title: Buffalo woman dies in her car after getting trapped for 18 hours while driving home from work
description: A 22-year-old woman caught in the middle of the historic winter storm in Buffalo, New York that has killed 27 in Erie County, alone, died while waiting in her car over the weekend.

title: House Committee publish Donald Trump redacted tax returns at MIDDAY after failed bid to keep private

title: Newport fire: Dozens of apartment residents evacuated after gas fire breaks out in shopping strip

title: Piers Morgan's Twitter account is HACKED by foul-mouthed troll calling for Somalian independence

title: North Lakes stabbing: Two youths to be charged over death of Emma Lovell north of Brisbane
